<header>{{> homeNavBar}}</header>
<main>
  <div class="phrase-container">
    <h1 class="phrase-h1">BEING</h1>
    <h3 class="phrase-h3">TONED IS IN STYLE...</h3>
  </div>
  <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
    <div class="carousel-inner">
      <div class="carousel-item active">
        <img
          class="carousel-img"
          src="../assets/images/fit-image1.png"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
          <p class="img-caption">
            I THINK IN LIFE YOU SHOULD WORK ON YOURSELF UNTIL THE DAY YOU DIE.
          </p>
          <p class="author-caption">SERENA WILLIAMS</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img
          class="carousel-img"
          src="../assets/images/fit-image2.png"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
          <p class="img-caption">
            I HATE EVERY MINUTE OF TRAINING. BUT I SAID, DON’T QUIT. SUFFER NOW
            AND LIVE THE REST OF YOUR LIFE AS A CHAMPION.
          </p>
          <p class="author-caption">MOHAMMAD ALI</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img
          class="carousel-img"
          src="../assets/images/fit-image3.png"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
          <p class="img-caption">
            I DIDN’T HAVE THE SAME FITNESS OR ABILITY AS OTHER GIRLS, SO I HAD
            TO BEAT THEM WITH MY MIND.
          </p>
          <p class="author-caption">MARTINA HINGIS</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img
          class="carousel-img"
          src="../assets/images/fit-image5.png"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
          <p class="img-caption">
            YOU’RE THE ONLY ONE WHO CAN MAKE THE DIFFERENCE. WHATEVER YOUR DREAM
            IS, GO FOR IT.
          </p>
          <p class="author-caption">MAGIC JOHNSON</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <img
          class="carousel-img"
          src="../assets/images/fit-image5.png"
          alt="..."
        />
        <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
          <p class="img-caption">
            I’VE ALWAYS BELIEVED THAT IF YOU PUT IN THE WORK, THE RESULTS WILL
            COME.
          </p>
          <p class="author-caption">MICHAEL JORDAN</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      class="carousel-control-prev"
      href="#carouselExampleControls"
      role="button"
      data-slide="prev"
    >
      <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a
      class="carousel-control-next"
      href="#carouselExampleControls"
      role="button"
      data-slide="next"
    >
      <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="btn-container">
    <button class="login-btn" id="login-btn" role="button">Login</button>
    <button class="signup-btn" id="signup-btn" role="button">Signup</button>
  </div>
</main>